{"id": "nos024", "name": "Audio_Evans_702_11_14", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_Conner", "Doorbell"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>Who is it?</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Are you Mr. Daniel Evans?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>Yes. And you are?</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "I am Vicky, a reporter from 08 Daily. This is my assistant. Here's our press passes.\nWe are currently doing a report on PAFF. We heard that you were her classmate when she studied at the Academy. We would like to ask you some questions. Could you spare us a few minutes?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>......\nI'm afraid there's nothing I can tell you people.</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Then...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>Please leave.</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Hey! Wai...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Mr. Evans! To be frank, we are currently investigating the whereabouts of the missing PAFF. And we are already very close to the truth.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>......!</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Hayato!</font>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Sis Vicky, let me handle this.</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "To be honest, we think that PAFF... Aroma's missing is deeply connected to her lost memories in the past. There may be some hidden information among all this. If she is caught up in something terrible, we will absolutely try our best to find out what it is. Please, lend us a hand!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>……</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>I've opened the door. You can take the left elevator to come upstairs.</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Hey, not bad at all! I didn't know you had this in you.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_Conner", "ドアベル"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>どちら様ですか？</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Daniel Evansさんでいらっしゃいますか？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>はい、そうですけど、あなたは？</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "私、08Dailyの記者をしております、Vickyと申します。\nこちらは私の助手です。\nこれが私の記者証です。\n実は、私たち最近PAFFの件に関して報道しておりまして、確かDanielさんは学生時代同級生だったとか……\nお話を伺わせていただくことはできますか？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>………\n何も話せることはないと思いますけど。</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "では……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>帰ってください。</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "あの！まっ……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Evansさん！実は今僕たちPAFFの行方を追っていて、しかも真相にかなり近づいているんです！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>……！</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">隼人！</font>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Vickyさん、任せてください。</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "僕たちは、PAFF……Aromaさんの失踪は、彼女が過去の記憶を失っていることと、大きく関係しているのではないかと考えています。\nそこに何かが隠されているのではないかと。\nもし彼女が何か事件に巻き込まれているのであれば、僕たちが必ず調べ上げます！\nお願いです！力を貸してください！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>ロックを解除しました。\n左のエレベーターから上がってきてください。</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "………！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "やるじゃない！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_Conner", "門鈴"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>哪位？</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Daniel Evans 先生嗎？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>是，你們是？</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "我是 08 Daily 的記者，Vicky，這位是我的助理。這是我們的記者證。\n我們現在正在做有關 PAFF 的報導，據說您是她學生時期的同學，想請教您一些問題，不知道方不方便？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>……。\n我恐怕沒有什麼能告訴你們的。</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "那……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>請回吧。</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "喂！等……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Evans 先生！其實我們現在正在追查失蹤的 PAFF 的下落，而且已經非常接近真相了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>……！</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Hayato！</font>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Vicky 姐，讓我來吧。</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "其實，我們認為 PAFF……Aroma 的失蹤跟她失去記憶的過去有很大的關係，這之中也許有什麼隱情。如果她被捲入了什麼不好的事情我們一定會想辦法查清楚，還請你幫幫我們！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>我開門了，你們搭左邊的電梯上來吧。</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "幹得不錯嘛！真看不出來啊你。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_Conner", "도어벨"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>누구세요?</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Daniel Evans 씨, 맞나요?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>네. 누구시죠?</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "08 Daily 소속 기자 Vicky라고 합니다. 그리고 이쪽은 제 조수고요. 이건 저희들의 기자증입니다.\n지금 PAFF와 관련해서 기사를 작성하고 있는데, Daniel 씨가 동창이라고 들었습니다. 그래서 몇 가지 좀 여쭤보고 싶은 게 있는데, 혹시 시간 좀 내어주실 수 있나요?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>...\n뭔가 해줄 수 있는 말이 없을 것 같은데요.</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "그렇다면...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>돌아가세요.</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "아! 잠깐만요...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Evans 씨! 사실 저희는 실종된 PAFF의 행방을 좇고 있습니다! 그리고 지금 거의 다 찾아낸 단계까지 왔어요.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>……！</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Hayato!</font>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Vicky 누나, 제게 맡겨요.</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "사실, 저희는 PAFF... 아니, Aroma의 실종은 그녀의 기억상실과 큰 연관이 있다고 보고 있어요. 분명 속 사정이 있었을 겁니다. 만약에라도 그녀가 더 나쁜 상황에 휘말리게 된다면, 저희는 어떻게든 방법을 찾아낼 겁니다. 그러니 그녀를 위해서도 도움을 주셨으면 합니다!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>......</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>문 열어놨어요. 좌측의 엘리베이터 타시고 올라오시면 됩니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "...!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "완전 잘했어! 너답지 않게 너무 잘해줬는데!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_Conner", "門鈴"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>哪位？</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Daniel Evans 先生嗎？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>是，你們是？</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "我是 08 Daily 的記者，Vicky，這位是我的助理。這是我們的記者證。\n我們現在正在做有關 PAFF 的報導，據說您是她學生時期的同學，想請教您一些問題，不知道方不方便？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>……。\n我恐怕沒有什麼能告訴你們的。</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "那……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>請回吧。</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "喂！等……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Evans 先生！其實我們現在正在追查失蹤的 PAFF 的下落，而且已經非常接近真相了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>……！</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Hayato！</font>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Vicky 姐，讓我來吧。</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "其實，我們認為 PAFF……Aroma 的失蹤跟她失去記憶的過去有很大的關係，這之中也許有什麼隱情。如果她被捲入了什麼不好的事情我們一定會想辦法查清楚，還請你幫幫我們！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>我開門了，你們搭左邊的電梯上來吧。</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "幹得不錯嘛！真看不出來啊你。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_Conner", "门铃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>哪位？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Daniel Evans 先生吗？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>是，你们是？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "我是 08 Daily 的记者，Vicky，这位是我的助理。这是我们的记者证。\n我们现在正在做有关 PAFF 的报导，据说您是她学生时期的同学，想请教您一些问题，不知道方不方便？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>……。\n我恐怕没有什么能告诉你们的。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "那……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>请回吧。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "喂！等……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Evans 先生！其实我们现在正在追查失踪的 PAFF 的下落，而且已经非常接近真相了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>……！ </i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Hayato！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Vicky 姐，让我来吧。 </font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "其实，我们认为 PAFF……Aroma 的失踪跟她失去记忆的过去有很大的关系，这之中也许有什么隐情。如果她被卷入了什么不好的事情我们一定会想办法查清楚，还请你帮帮我们！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>……。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Daniel]"], "content": "<i>我开门了，你们搭左边的电梯上来吧。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "干得不错嘛！真看不出来啊你。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}